OL,3,CDeputy PM rejects US State Department
OL,4,Ccomments on UK 'two-tier' policing
OL,6,FThe Deputy Prime Minister has said
OL,7,Fthat he doesn't "recognise" the idea
OL,8,Fthat the UK has a two-tier policing
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News on Friday
OL,12,Fmorning, David Lammy was responding to
OL,13,Fa post made on X by the US State
OL,14,FDepartment implying that the UK was in
OL,15,F"civilisational decline" as a result
OL,16,Fof "ideological conditioning and two-
OL,17,Ftiered policing".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
