OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780747879
OL,3,CDeputy PM rejects US State Department
OL,4,Ccomments on UK 'two-tier' policing
OL,6,FThe message comes after the murder of
OL,7,F18-year-old Henry Nowak, which has
OL,8,Ftriggered a political row that spilled
OL,9,Fout onto the streets of Southampton on
OL,10,FTuesday night in violent protests over
OL,11,Fthe police's handling of the case.
OL,13,FMr Nowak's killer Vickrum Digwa
OL,14,Fclaimed he had been the victim of a
OL,15,Fracist attack. While Mr Nowak was
OL,16,Fhandcuffed by police who ignored his
OL,17,Fpleas that he could not breathe as he
OL,18,Flay dying.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780747879
OL,3,CDeputy PM rejects US State Department
OL,4,Ccomments on UK 'two-tier' policing
OL,6,FThe State Department went on to send
OL,7,Fcondolences to Mr Nowak's family and
OL,8,Fthe UK.
OL,10,FThe Deputy PM acknowledged the message
OL,11,Fof condolence and insisted that the US
OL,12,Fand UK enforcement "work very closely
OL,13,Ftogether" but rejected the notion of
OL,14,Ftwo-tier policing, saying: "I do not
OL,15,Frecognise the caricature."
OL,17,FMr Lammy defended the police saying
OL,18,Fthat forces across the UK "are doing
OL,19,Fall that they can to bear down on
OL,20,Fcrime".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780747879
OL,3,CDeputy PM rejects US State Department
OL,4,Ccomments on UK 'two-tier' policing
OL,6,FWhen asked about this highly
OL,7,Funconventional intervention from the
OL,8,FUS, David Lammy acknowledged that
OL,9,Fthere is a "particular way that Donald
OL,10,FTrump pursues his points".
OL,12,FHe went on to explain that in this
OL,13,Fparticular case "it is right" that
OL,14,Fthere is an investigation into
OL,15,Fpolicing handling of Mr Nowak's death.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
