OL,3,CDeputy PM rejects US State Department
OL,4,Ccomments on UK 'two-tier' policing
OL,6,FThe police watchdog is expected to
OL,7,Freport on the case within the next
OL,8,Fthree months. The Independent Office
OL,9,Ffor Police Conduct (IOPC) said its
OL,10,Findependent investigation "remains
OL,11,Fongoing".
OL,13,FIt added that investigators are
OL,14,Fexamining a large amount of body-worn
OL,15,Fvideo as well as material presented
OL,16,Fduring Digwa's trial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
